Business Brief -- UST Inc.:
   Fourth-Quarter Net Income
   Rose 21% to $66.3 Million
For the year, UST's said its profit increased 19% to
$265.9 million, or $1.18 a share, from $223.3 million, or 98
cents a share, in 1990. All per-share figures reflect a
2-for-1 stock split announced in December. Sales rose 19% to
$907.3 million from $764.7 million.